description: Enzo (NZO) is a social currency created for Alfa, a patented hyperlocal social network that connects people base on what they do using a blockchain calendar. Together, Alfa and Enzo, brings the vision of a unified global operating environment to life. It aims to deliver mass adoption for cryptocurrency and foster the right conditions for Ambient Computing to emerge. By combining marketplace, social networking, and search into a new experience, the organization expects to be able to compete with aging giants: Facebook, Alibaba, Amazon, Apple, and Google.
name: Enzo
